Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Naima Dora Troina
AuthorCountry: Italy
Text: I have not yet begun to write my story because I think I do not have enough
  experience, this trip could be my chance to take out what I need from myself, and
  write it down. Because only by traveling can I really feel happy and complete.
